            "His poetry explored primevalism and humanity's origins.",
            "Primevalism often appears in discussions of myth and mythic memory."
          ],
          "collocations": ["primevalism in art", "primevalism movement"],
          "synonyms": ["primordialism", "primitivism"],
          "antonyms": [],
